            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18967405-loretta?shelf=my-2020-reading-challenge">my-2020-reading-challenge</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18967405-loretta?shelf=plays">plays</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/18967405-loretta?shelf=may-2020">may-2020</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2737862786" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16267454528351723408">Meh. I’m usually not into books/plays of this ilk where a writer takes a real person and puts their spin on the person and events. I would much rather read a biography of Joan of Arc which I will probably do.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


